## Installing the Necessary Packages

  - VS Code: pip install kagglehub pandas matplotlib
  - Google Collab: pip install kagglehub 
  
### If You Face Permission Issues
  - Head to Kaggle.com
  - Go to Kagle Account Settings
  - Scroll to API and click "Create New API Token" (This will download the kaggle.json file)
  -  Place kaggle.json in:
    - Windows: C:\Users\<YourUser>\.kaggle\kaggle.json
    - Mac/Linux: ~/.kaggle/kaggle.json
